{"tid":741352,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ALL IN 哈利卡尼神射手，好過收息，世界杯發達靠呢鋪","createTime":"2018-07-13T14:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T18:23:41.000Z","uid":43785,"like":155,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"d40024f0015aa2b6505afb0ec65ad1b1230ad81a","tid":741352,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/224735_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F224735_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7cff2332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二名盧卡古聽晚要入三球先贏到佢。<br />\n可能性近乎零。<br />\n<br />\nALL IN 哈利卡尼神射手，好過收息，等多一晚收錢。<br />\n有幾多買幾多,輸幾多贏番馬會幾多。<br />\n依家唔買，錯過左小心馬會賠唔起要學騎師王玩封盤。<br />\n<br />\n做窮人定有錢人，你決定。<br />\n記住，有膽先可以做大事，冇膽一事無成。"},{"pid":"447e5a9f0fb34dad80da123904f139529ba4bf1a","tid":741352,"uid":43785,"like":91,"dislike":5,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講乜撚野風險，<br />\n盧卡古入三球反勝既機率，係零呀<br />\n<br />\n比利時呢幾場腳軟，莫講三球，一球都未必入到啦佢。"},{"pid":"50df210971d919b70448f7aeee926cf626fb8dd2","tid":741352,"uid":43785,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"夏薩特要爭取表現，隨時獨食唔分波自己射。<br />\n盧卡古想贏都係算把啦。"},{"pid":"bc4e94a720371a5bea0d63b78cef7ba73660aa59","tid":741352,"uid":71578,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3584d9e62e9aa50d29f7679b293429b9bd235540","tid":741352,"uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":31,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"bc4e94a720371a5bea0d63b78cef7ba73660aa59","tid":741352,"uid":71578,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啦，ON咩鳩<br />\n我俾條必中公式你，<br />\n你跟就跟，冇錢